*/ public class FileRegistrationRequest extends DefaultFileRegistrationRequest { private Long referenceId; //for the case when the resource is located s3 private Long fileS3BucketId; // private BiologicalDataItemResourceType fileType; public Long getReferenceId() { return referenceId; } public void setReferenceId(Long referenceId) { this.referenceId = referenceId; } public Long getS3BucketId() { return fileS3BucketId; } public void setS3BucketId(Long s3BucketId) { this.fileS3BucketId = s3BucketId; } public BiologicalDataItemResourceType getType() { return fileType; } public void setType(BiologicalDataItemResourceType type) { this.fileType = type; } }// function below has no smell
